@startuml
title ZeKin 三类打卡业务时序图
skinparam backgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam shadowing false
robust "查寝打卡" as Dorm
robust "上课打卡" as Class
robust "实习打卡" as Intern
robust "教师审核" as Review

@0
Dorm is "未开放"
Class is "未开放"
Intern is "未开放"
Review is "待处理"

@8
Intern is "可提交"

@8.5
Class is "课前窗口"

@9
Class is "已关闭/等待下节课"

@18
Intern is "已关闭"

@22
Dorm is "可提交"

@23
Dorm is "已关闭"
Review is "集中审核"

@24
Review is "完成或次日继续"

legend right
MVP不强制实现复杂时间表引擎；
本图用于描述业务窗口和验收口径。
endlegend
@enduml
